**Justification:**

The agent incorrectly determined that the user was **eligible** for Child Benefit, when the expected outcome is **Not Eligible**.

The critical error lies in the agent's assessment of the education requirement. The agent stated that "The child is in college studying for GCSEs (which counts as approved education)" without verifying the crucial detail of study hours.

